      <title>英国《金融时报》称，谷歌正在考虑对人工智能驱动的搜索功能收取费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/google-considers-charging-for-ai-fueled-search-features-ft-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据英国《金融时报》报道，谷歌正在考虑对人工智能运行的新“高级”功能收费，这标志着谷歌首次将其任何核心产品置于付费专区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/google-considers-charging-for-ai-fueled-search-features-ft-says</guid>
